STEPS TO ACHIEVE:
    1. make sure that at least all the needed colors are in the palette
    2. start from pages, header and layouts first - focus on cleaning unused styles and seeing that the theme is working
    3. proceed to components, like form cards in main page
    4. implement the icons for the fields
    5. implement the popup component
    6. after you're done, check EVERYTHING :)

MISSIONS:
