    APPLIES TO ALL:
        ☐ remove inline styles and unused css!!!!
        ☐ components like inputs are all the same across the site (colors, border radius and color) - make sure to configure them in the theme
        - if icons/images are missing, add them
        - avoid using inline style (like sx) and css unless necessary so the components will use the theme
        - if inline style is needed, use colors from the palette like this:
            const { theme } = useTheme();
            ...
            <div style={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }} />
        - keep it simple and readable
        - DO NOT use colors if they are not in the palette - if a color is missing, add it to the palette
        - do some testing as you go to see that everything is responsive

