    POPUPS:
        ☐ create a base popup component, for example: (just look at how they look in figma)
            <container>
                <image?/>
                <text/>
                <buttons/>
            </container>
        the popup should receive props like:
            - title: string
            v if empty won't be displayed
            - content?: string or element
            - image?: path to image
            - mainButton?: {
            -   text: string
            -   onClick: function
            -   buttonProps: ButtonProps (for disabled and more if needed)
            -   }
            - cancelButton?: {
            -   text: string
            -   onClick: function
            -   buttonProps: ButtonProps
            -   }
        ☐ title should be 24px and 600 weight
        ☐ mainButton should be filled, cancelButton should be outlined
        ☐ if the popup is too big, it should be scrollable
        ☐ popup should be centered
        ☐ replace the current popups using the new one